cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper is primarily focused on developing a machine learning system for controlling a robotic manipulator using visual perception only. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also extensively uses deep reinforcement learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and computer vision techniques, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with the control of a physical system, which could also make it relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
